  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">The Wizard spawns by the ramp on the way to the Jailer's room.  There are several goblins around the ramp.  Just kill them till he spawns.  Can spawn elsewherre as well, but is common to the ramp.<br>
<br>
This zone is a blast to hunt in, at least until you get too close and the Ice Giants decide to summon you.  So be careful in the King Room, and if a high level group is pulling IG's, go to a different room. <br>
<br>
Slay well,<br>
VInaddar Slashall  DE warrior of 42 seasons of evil<br><br></td></tr>
