  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">Getting in through the front is not easy.  Ice Giants, (Red to me) roam there.  However, there is another entrance up on the North wall, east of the east-fork of the river (right in the corner).  If you go through there, you don't need camo or invis because there are no goblins in the tunnel.  You come out through a secret door in the wall - just past the giants....turn left there and you are in....just be careful once you zone - Goblins galore!!<br><br></td></tr>
