  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">I was looking over the maps/loot of this zone, and it's be perfect for a group of 6 level 30's. The agroing greens Im sure are annoying, but nothing to worry about with a good enchanter with his AE Mezmerize spell ( as long as the group doesn't just decide to attack whatever they want...) It seems they could kill everything up to the king quiet easily.  Here's what I think of a "Perfect Group" for in here: Monk, Druid, Bard, Enchanter, Necro, and another Bard or Necro.  A Pair of bards twisiting heal song/fight song is great, and a pair of level 30 necro pets could prolly solo anything in this zone! Enchanter for Clarity/crowd controll/quickening, bards/druids for healing and speed, and necros for the dammage. Monks is there to do what Monks always do: kill things real quick :) Anyway, I'm hoping to get a group like this together, and since it's always empty, we could take it all :)  Good Luck with you adventures!<br><br></td></tr>
